{"title":"笔","authors":["李文富"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骆驼营水泥厂工人　李文富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔，磨秃了的笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸上画满了字迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又捡起一根铁条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划着车间的空白地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几双眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投射在一个图案上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几个人的心弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨动着一个频率。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着一个个难关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目盯着一道道难题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写呀、画呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁条指向了不同的标记。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样，才能提高产量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样，才能质量第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家抬起头来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉宇间充满了笑意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看每小时仅仅增产零点一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，一天呢，一月呢，一年呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算算这道题！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几颗心紧紧连在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几只手合拿一枝“笔”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画呀、画呀！画的是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗，勤俭建国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生，奋发图强建设社会主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《锦铁消息》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}